Relationship adviser and blogger, Joro Olumofin has shared the story of a man who has been secretly sleeping with his younger sister consensually. According to him, the sister is the only female he has been with all his life and he is not interested in anyone else. It should be noted that his sister is presently seeing another man who has no knowledge of their sexual history. The revelations of the man has shook the internet considering the fact that such an act is considered incest in a religious society like Nigeria. Read his account below: His second mesage: His initial message to Joro Source